reviewText:
Poorly written and woefully inaccurate in its facts. About as factual as Donald Trump's DD 214.
Don't waste your time, or money on this stinker.
Mike Wilson, CDR, USN, Ret
Really liked this documentary, it was enlightening.
Dont waste your money on this one, poorly researched, inaccurate data.  How hard would it be to figure out how many personnel were on board the 109 that night?
